{"talk":{"id":48919,"name":"Rose M. Mutiso: How to bring affordable, sustainable electricity to Africa","description":"Energy poverty, or the lack of access to electricity and other basic energy services, affects nearly two-thirds of Sub-Saharan Africa. As the region's population continues to increase, so will the need to build a new energy system to grow with it, says Rose M. Mutiso. In a bold talk, she discusses how a balanced mix of solutions like solar, wind farms, geothermal power and modern grids could create a high-energy future for Africa -- providing reliable electricity, creating jobs and raising incomes.","slug":"rose_m_mutiso_how_to_bring_affordable_sustainable_electricity_to_africa","recorded_at":"2019-07-20 00:00:00","published_at":"2019-10-28 14:50:11","updated_at":"2021-04-09 19:31:20","viewed_count":0,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":603,"name":"TEDSummit 2019"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/2e4378a53d7806ad9d92f97e13cfc28b128f84d2_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/2e4378a53d7806ad9d92f97e13cfc28b128f84d2_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/2e4378a53d7806ad9d92f97e13cfc28b128f84d2_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/2e4378a53d7806ad9d92f97e13cfc28b128f84d2_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/de0e8882099f3b5bb33b3a632183d35a4c9701eb_2880x1620.jpg","media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/RoseMMutiso_2019T-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":6452505,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/RoseMMutiso_2019T-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":17822012,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/RoseMMutiso_2019T-320k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4f